headline: The Sharks are Coming: Clover & Sony Pictures Television Reveal Star-Studded Line Up for the First-Ever Live Clover x Shark Tank Summit in Las Vegas
summary: LAS VEGAS, July 08, 2025--Today, Clover, the world's smartest all-in-one point-of-sale system, and Sony Pictures Television (SPT), which produces the critically acclaimed, multi-Emmy Award-winning "Shark Tank," announce legendary entrepreneurs, dealmakers, and brand builders from the Shark Tank universe as featured speakers for the first-ever live, Clover x Shark Tank Summit.
